001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.bluetooth;
002
003public final class BluetoothConstants {
004    public final static String DEVICE_NAME_TSLIM_X2 = "tslim X2";
005
006    // note, the Bluetooth DIS device name still identifies as a X2.
007    // Only the user-visible name is labeled as "Tandem Mobi"
008    public final static String DEVICE_NAME_TANDEM_MOBI = "Tandem Mobi";
009
010    public static boolean isTandemBluetoothDevice(String deviceName) {
011        return deviceName.startsWith(DEVICE_NAME_TSLIM_X2) || deviceName.startsWith(DEVICE_NAME_TANDEM_MOBI);
012    }
013}
